# 🚀 Real Production Troubleshooting Flow

Most DevOps Engineers follow this sequence during production issues:

```text
1. Check Pod Status
2. Describe Pod
3. Check Logs
4. Check Events
5. Verify Service & Endpoints
6. Verify Node Health
7. Verify Storage / Network / RBAC
```

